        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This black *+2 striking scimitar* reflects light only along its edge, like a thin crescent moon. It grants a +1 item bonus to Stealth while you're holding it, increasing to a +2 item bonus if it has a *+3 weapon potency rune*.",
